      <title>LME 禁止新的俄罗斯金属，但为大量旧库存做好准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-13/lme-bans-new-russian-metal-but-braces-for-a-flood-of-old-stock</link>
